{"tid":90512,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇同好鐘意cnblue？入黎討論下","createTime":"2017-01-22T06:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T16:55:18.000Z","uid":78418,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d346428c2b1aa43527e7ec76070dbc5ef1d45eeb","tid":90512,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"請大家理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以唔鐘意 但請唔好係post屌其他人 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請忽視我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年係佢地出道既第七年喇<br />\n時間過得真係快<br />\n唔經唔覺做boice都做左3年<br />\n<br />\n有冇人係由孤獨的人開始追到宜加？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411da7d15a7e8e23cd5d32cd2d0ea39a52131a1a","tid":90512,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"無留意佢地 不過好耐以前聽過佢地有首野好似叫Victoria 果首幾正 以前loop左排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac3de7d9eba44ecfc11ea24030eae7789919c94","tid":90512,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"係咪出live個陣結他唔插電套鼓冇pedal個隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b7388365459d904655486fbf6b228f60b2d4ea","tid":90512,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無留意佢地 不過好耐以前聽過佢地有首野好似叫Victoria 果首幾正 以前loop左排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首就係孤獨的人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢地首首都幾正架"},{"pid":"4596728c3f0989ee85ec067541e7d52d7c0ac51f","tid":90512,"uid":10129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人開Cnblue post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji